Before your click on "Activate", there are several warm notes : 
	1. After the click on "Activate my account", go to Account/Settings
	2. Click "change" below the defualt picture (Sorry I have no control over the default picture). 
	3. Redicted to a page called "Gravatars", which is a sub-website of WordPress.com.
	4. Log in with your WordPress account. If you don't have, create one with current email address.
	5. Click "Add email address" to add your Footprint account email address
	6. Gravatars will send you an email to verify your email address. Click the link inside the verifying email.
	7. You are now able to upload your profile image by clicking "Add a new image"
	8. Follow the lateron instructions.
	9. Back to and refresh your Footprint profile page

